  "readme": "# A Neovim Tool for Pi\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://pi.dev\">\n    <img alt=\"pi logo\" src=\"https://pi.dev/logo-auto.svg\" width=\"128\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n> A Pi extension providing a __`discover_neovim`__ Tool for __[Pi](https://pi.dev)__ to find __[Neovim](https://neovim.io)__ instances, and select which one to interact with (using [Neovim's RPC API](https://neovim.io/doc/user/api) through tools such as [pi-msgpack-rpc](https://github.com/paperlib/pi-msgpack-rpc).)\n\n---\n<img width=\"1450\" height=\"1032\" alt=\"pi-neovim-screenshot\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/719ea7aa-205f-4b5a-9080-d07889155d4e\" />\n",
